        <h1>Battle For Leaf Village</h1>
        <span class="gamemore">Developer: <span class="gameauth"><a href="https://www.snokido.com/author/cartoon-network">Cartoon Network</a> </span>&nbsp; - &nbsp; <span class="gamehit">224 788</span> plays</span>
        <p id="desc" class="gamedesc">Naruto must face a grave danger once again. Orochimaru raised an army right in the middle of his Chunin exams and is now preparing to attack Konoha. Naruto must draw on all of his strengths and techniques to fight and triumph over Orochimaru’s forces of evil. Cross through the game’s many different regions and tackle countless enemies in this RPG set in the famous animated series’ world.</p>        <div class="gametags">
          <a href="https://www.snokido.com/games/rpg">RPG</a> <a href="https://www.snokido.com/games/anime">Anime</a> <a href="https://www.snokido.com/games/naruto">Naruto</a> <a href="https://www.snokido.com/games/heroes">Heroes</a> <a href="https://www.snokido.com/games/ninja">Ninja</a>        </div>
